abstract: Brawl erupts in Ukrainian Parliament after Prime Min Arseniy P Yatsenyuk appears to anger Parliament member Oleg Barna.
lead_paragraph: This brawl was particularly fierce, erupting after the prime minister was physically lifted by a member of an opposing party.

headline.main: The Gloves Come Off, Again, in Ukraine’s Parliament
